title: Taylor, Wilson top Stonewall in four
text:
Taylor, Wilson top Stonewall in four Staff Report 9 p.m. EDT October 15, 2015 File CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
QUICKSBURG â€” Abby Taylor powered down 20 kills and added 13 aces to lead Wilson Memorial's volleyball team past Stonewall Jackson in four sets on Thursday, 25-8, 25-17, 21-25, 25-20. 
Addison Tuttle added seven kills and two blocks while Hannah Johnson contributed six kills and 18 assists. 
Emma Hilbert and Grace Carter both had six digs. 
Wilson completed the sweep, taking the jayvee match 25-17, 25-23. Read or Share this story: http://www.newsleader.com/story/sports/2015/10/15/taylor-wilson-top-stonewall-four/74024522/ TOP VIDEOS
